data.description: Great opportunity to own a 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 1 car garage home with large backyard in popular South Venice! Home features a new roof in 2023, new windows in 2017, new A/C 2017, shower glass door 2023, insulated garage side steel door in 2020, new tiles on lanai in 2022. Close proximity to dining, shops, beaches, Downtown Venice, and a short distance to Downtown Sarasota, Sarasota Airport, and Sarasota Memorial Hospital.
